OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA sunny and
OL,6,Fvery warm evening for many. Overnight
OL,7,Fit will remain warm with clear skies
OL,8,Ffor most areas, especially central and
OL,9,Fsouthern parts of the UK. Scotland and
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland though will see cloud
OL,11,Fincrease later.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FAnother sunny day across
OL,14,FEngland and Wales as the heatwave
OL,15,Fcontinues, with a small chance of a
OL,16,Ffew heavy, thundery showers. Fresher
OL,17,Ffor Scotland and Northern Ireland with
OL,18,Fsunny spells.
